            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>北京时间 3 月 1 日 4:30，国王杯半决赛次回合，马德里竞技客场挑战毕尔巴鄂竞技，赛前双方首发公布。</p><p><img data-width="750" data-height="300" src="https://bdimg6.qunliao.info/fastdfs7/M00/4D/76/rBUC6GXghwWAQPq1AAC_whQ6o-w772.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></p><p><img data-width="1080" data-height="1350" src="https://bdimg6.qunliao.info/fastdfs7/M00/49/6D/rBUBsmXg2SiANU87AAXjcRpjpbs548.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></p><p><img data-width="1080" data-height="1350" src="https://bdimg6.qunliao.info/fastdfs7/M00/4D/96/rBUC6GXg2SiARXhHAAaL8qWTRXY424.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></p>]]>
